Expressions like `o.m().method()` or `o.m().attribute` or `o.attr.method()` or `o.attr.attribute` are illegal.

frontmatter.shortDescription: Attribute accesses cannot be chained together
frontmatter.shortCorrection: Attribute accesses can be chained together
